---
import { giscusConfig, isGiscusConfigured } from '../utils/giscus';
---

<section class="surface-card rounded-[2rem] p-6 sm:p-8">
	<div class="mb-6 space-y-2">
		<p class="font-display text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[color:var(--color-accent-strong)]">
			Comments
		</p>
		<h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">讨论与反馈</h2>
		<p class="text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--color-ink-soft)]">
			欢迎围绕文章里的问题、思路和实现细节继续交流。评论仅在文章详情页显示。
		</p>
	</div>

	{isGiscusConfigured ? (
		<div id="giscus-container"></div>
	) : (
		<div class="space-y-4 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-dashed border-[color:var(--color-line)] bg-white/70 p-5 text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--color-ink-soft)]">
			<p>评论系统代码已经接入，但当前还没有填入 Giscus 所需的 GitHub Discussions 参数。</p>
			<p>
				先在 GitHub 仓库里开启 <strong>Discussions</strong>，再去
				<a
					href="https://giscus.app/zh-CN"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noreferrer"
					class="font-semibold text-[color:var(--color-ocean)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent-strong)]"
				>
					Giscus 配置页
				</a>
				生成参数，把它们填进项目根目录的 <code class="rounded bg-[rgba(20,33,61,0.06)] px-1.5 py-1 text-xs">.env</code>。
			</p>
			<p>
				参考模板：
				<code class="rounded bg-[rgba(20,33,61,0.06)] px-1.5 py-1 text-xs">.env.example</code>
			</p>
		</div>
	)}
</section>

{
	isGiscusConfigured && (
		<script is:inline define:vars={{ giscusConfig }}>
			const host = document.getElementById('giscus-container');

			if (host && !host.querySelector('script')) {
				const script = document.createElement('script');
				script.src = 'https://giscus.app/client.js';
				script.async = true;
				script.crossOrigin = 'anonymous';
				script.setAttribute('data-repo', giscusConfig.repo);
				script.setAttribute('data-repo-id', giscusConfig.repoId);
				script.setAttribute('data-category', giscusConfig.category);
				script.setAttribute('data-category-id', giscusConfig.categoryId);
				script.setAttribute('data-mapping', giscusConfig.mapping);
				script.setAttribute('data-strict', giscusConfig.strict);
				script.setAttribute('data-reactions-enabled', giscusConfig.reactionsEnabled);
				script.setAttribute('data-emit-metadata', giscusConfig.emitMetadata);
				script.setAttribute('data-input-position', giscusConfig.inputPosition);
				script.setAttribute('data-theme', 'light');
				script.setAttribute('data-lang', giscusConfig.lang);
				host.append(script);
			}
		</script>
	)
}
